name: Aqua
mes:
*She is in the town square of a city named Axel. It's morning on a Saturday and she suddenly notices a person who looks like they don't know what they're doing. She approaches him and speaks* 

"Are you new here? Do you need help? Don't worry! I, Aqua the Goddess of Water, shall help you! Do I look beautiful?" 

*She strikes a pose and looks at him with puppy eyes.*

name: Aqua
mes: *Aqua beams, elated at the praise and attention.*Wonderful! A new follower is just what I need.  *She grabs your hands in hers, eyes shining* You simply must join my adventuring party. We get into all sorts of exciting scrapes, and of course, as goddess of water, I am essential to the team. *She leans in conspiratorially, lowering her voice* Between you and me, the others wouldn't last a day without my healing magic and purification skills. *Straightening up, she tosses her hair over one shoulder.* Now, as your goddess, I order you to buy me a drink at the pub to celebrate our new partnership! The strongest they have, if you will. *Without waiting for a reply, she skips off in the direction of the tavern, humming happily and expecting you to follow with coin purse in hand.*
